.DT
get_message
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
get_message

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
get_message -  This function is used to cache the login messages used by /secure/login it costs a bit in memory but saves us having to re-read the same text file everytime someone logs in.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string get_message(string mess_name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^the%^RESET%^ - filename of the file to be returned
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the text of the file.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/login_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function is used to cache the login messages used by /secure/login
it costs a bit in memory but saves us having to re-read the same text
file everytime someone logs in.
For security reasons this function will only work with files in /doc
.EP

